<br>
Basically, what you do is to form up a Pull group (usually a bard for pulling and a tank with an insanely high Magic resist, cleric, enchanter, wizard, and one other), a debuff group (shamans, enchanters, mages etc) as many other groups you feel necessary (typically 6 groups or so will work).  Make sure you bring as many Ice based casters as you can.<br>
<br>
Now, the tactic.  Position the Main tank in the open are just before the path to the Burning Woods zone and have the debuff group stationed up on the hill to the left if you are facing away from the BW zone.  Then have everyone else stand back behind the small hill leading to the BW zone.  The bard will then pull Talendor (usually takes about 2 minutes or so for Talendor to arrive to the killing spot).  Once he reaches the Main tank, the main tank needs to immediately attack him eating the first fear (remember Fear has a 30 second recycle time).  As the main tank engages him the debuff group starts throwing all the debuffs at him that they can.  Once the first fear goes off the Main tank will shout for every one else to charge.  Tanks that are there do a typical Zerg-type attack while the casters chain-nuke with Ice based spells.  The object is to take him down before his next fear goes off.  If the second fear goes off it's pretty much over try to zone to BW if possible and set up to try again.  <br>
<br>
Last time we did this the fight took 16 seconds (I timed it from the &quot;charge&quot;).  Also, Gorenaire works pretty much the same way except you need Fire based spells and Cold resist. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showMessageRange?topicID=120.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showMessage?topicID=130.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.showMessage?topicID=73.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.emailToFriend?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.threadControl?topicID=120.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovefrm20.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=120.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm18">FAQ & Index<option valu